            "heading": "Our Arccos Smart Grips Bundle game tracking system includes:",
            "content": "<ul><li>13 grips of your choice with ultra-light embedded weather resistant sensors. Featuring a long lasting battery and power saving mode. Includes 2 year warranty.</li><li>1 smart putter sensor that twists into the top of your putter grip</li><li>1 Link Pro - Automatically track shots right from your front pocket, without a phone. Lightweight shot tracking device syncs with the Arccos app. Includes a wireless charging case that provides safe storage and powers up to 12 rounds.</li><li>1st year's membership to the award winning Arccos app* (New Members only).</li><li>Annual Free Sensor Renewal Program: Get 5 new smart sensors every year to use on additional clubs or as replacements. <a href=\"https://arccos-dev.myshopify.com/blogs/community/arccos-member-free-sensors-program\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Arccos Member Free Sensors Program\">Learn More.</a></li><li>The latest shot tracking software on both iOS and Android platforms.</li></ul>",
