            "heading": "The smartest way to improve your golf game with:",
            "content": "<ul><li>A.I. Powered GPS Rangefinder: Get precise yardages adjusted in real time for wind, elevation/slope, temperature, humidity & altitude.</li><li>Smart Club Distances: Know how far you really hit all your clubs in every situation.</li><li>Strokes Gained Insights: Pinpoint your strengths and weaknesses based on your target handicap, so you know exactly which part of your game to work on.</li><li>Personal A.I. Caddie Advice: Real-time insights into optimal & alternative strategies, as well as outcome predictions, for every shot.</li><li>New In Play user experience with live, high resolution maps including 3D, faster course updates, new zoom functionality.</li></ul>",
